column5: Did anyone hear the latest news? They are thinking of turning Parts of the Island into a red light district(legal prostitution). What does everyone think of that? I think that they'd at least have to move center Island first!  Or did anyone see the New frozen burgers called Webers???I wonder if they are the same webers on hwy 11!!!!
wow, where did u hear this from?
LOL thats a good one.    dsn
It's gonna be hard to get skunked there now !
Now you'll need to get biohazard gear just in case you get into some of those legendary Coney Island Whitefish!!!! Yikes...  RJ
Might even start to smell like one.
LOL....heard this on 680 news....it was introduced by one councellor, but pretty much shot down immediately.  It'll never happen
Guess I gotta get my new gear ready then (ok so I'm not much of a photoshopper )
They can't move the squatters off the Island...they sure can't move more on.....
"Guess I gotta get my new gear ready then"     LOL - babyyyyyyyyyy!   lol

If it happens, be careful: - you may catch something other than fish - the place may smell 'fishier' and - no one is going to believe you went to the island to fish - the place is going to get that much more crowded Probably a bad idea
21 years ago I was unfortunate enough to discover a nude gay beach on the island.  No sir, won't go back not even for fishing.  Ouch, 21 years ago man am I getting old
